FeedAgregator
=============
RSS and Atom feed agregator in desktop widgets + notifications
--------------------------------------------------------------
Copyright 2018-2019 Juliette Monsel <j_4321@protonmail.com>

Changelog
---------

-Version 1.3.1
    * Fix widget disappearance in Plasma desktop
    * Fix requirements in setup.py 
    * Wrap/unwrap entries by clicking anywhere on their titles

-Version 1.3.0
    * Make image loading timeout customizable
    * Fix error when an image cannot be loaded
    * Add help dialog
    * Improve detection of already running instances (less often ask to delete pidfile)
    
- Version 1.2.0
    * Improve style
    * Add scrollbar to widgets
    * Add hide button to widgets
    * Add possibility to deactivate feeds from manager
    * Add color preview in config dialog
    * Add copy on Ctrl+C in html frame
    * Save config more often to avoid loosing info in case of crash
    * Fix ValueError in after_cancel 

- Version 1.1.3
    * Fix PhotoImage import in trayicon.tkicon

- Version 1.1.2
    * Fix error in messagebox due to the use of PIL.ImageTk

- Version 1.1.1
    * Reduce left margin of bullet points in feed entries
    * Change feed data saving because the content is not always compatible with configparser
    * Use PIL.ImageTk to handle more image formats in feed entries

- Version 1.1.0
    * Display time in locale timezone instead of UTC
    * Update feeds immediately after changing update delay
    * Add update feed entry in menu
    * Fix widgets position and stickyness
    * Improve entry sorting
    * Add categories

- Version 1.0.1
    * Fix update checker
    * Rename feed from widget

- Version 1.0.0
    * Initial release
